66
00:03:32,958 --> 00:03:34,583
Hey, long time no see.

67
00:03:34,666 --> 00:03:35,541
[TOHRU]
Hello.

68
00:03:35,625 --> 00:03:37,375
[BOY A]
It's the cosplay lady!

69
00:03:37,458 --> 00:03:38,958
That's me!
Have a good one!

70
00:03:39,041 --> 00:03:42,291
[KOBAYASHI] This dragon's better
at being social than me!

71
00:03:42,375 --> 00:03:44,500
