He's got my purse!

97
00:04:44,333 --> 00:04:46,375
Do you mind? May I get him?

98
00:04:46,458 --> 00:04:48,625
[KOBAYASHI]
What? I dunno.

99
00:04:48,708 --> 00:04:52,083
