That coulda been way worse.

116
00:05:35,916 --> 00:05:38,666
[FISHMONGER A]
She's keeping us safe! [laughs]

117
00:05:38,750 --> 00:05:41,375
[TOHRU giggles]

118
00:05:48,916 --> 00:05:51,375
[TOHRU]
So, um... That was scary.

119
00:05:51,458 --> 00:05:54,291
[KOBAYASHI]
I was stressing a bit, myself.

120
00:05:54,375 --> 00:05:57,958
Sorry. I should have
told you to hold back more.

121
00:05:58,041 --> 00:05:59,375
