that hand for a while...

127
00:06:33,708 --> 00:06:36,791
[TOHRU hums]

128
00:06:36,875 --> 00:06:37,875
[KOBAYASHI]
What's your tail like?

129
00:06:37,958 --> 00:06:40,541
[TOHRU]
Uh. Oh, it's sweet and creamy!

130
00:06:40,625 --> 00:06:42,416
[KOBAYASHI]
Astounding humility.

131
00:06:49,625 --> 00:06:51,458
[doorbell rings]

132
00:06:51,541 --> 00:06:54,000
Must be my delivery.

133
00:06:54,083 --> 00:06:55,125
Hello?

134
00:07:00,291 --> 00:07:01,375
[KOBAYASHI]
Hmm?

135
00:07:03,625 --> 00:07:06,375
[KOBAYASHI] So this is
what I let into my house.

136
00:07:06,458 --> 00:07:08,916
This girl-thing has
to be Tohru's friend.

137
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:12,250
She's got horns and a tail, too.

138
00:07:12,333 --> 00:07:15,416
