--You cuckold.

147
00:07:34,958 --> 00:07:37,166
--[KOBAYASHI] Hmm?
--You slut in glasses!

148
00:07:37,250 --> 00:07:39,375
Okay, pretty sure
you're making a mistake.

149
00:07:39,458 --> 00:07:40,500
